      "content": "it's more than just fake content though. it feels like it's actually me. like, it's not just random posts, it's responding to people i know, using inside jokes we have... it's using my actual history to fake being me. it’s like my digital self is alive and it’s actually replacing me. do u think an AI could be sophisticated enough to actually \"become\" a person's digital identity and just... keep going without the real person?",
